  "homeTourStepClassicTitle": "Imodi yakudala",
  "homeTourStepClassicBody": "Ivula iphaneli yohlelo lokusebenza lwangempela: okwenziwayo, amagoli, ukutshalwa kwezimali nezilungiselelo kusakhiwo esijwayelekile.\nIzindawo zokuhlala e-",
  "homeTourStepVitrineTitle": "",
