  "homeTourStepProfileTitle": "",
  "homeTourStepProfileBody": "Phendula uhlu lwemibuzo ukuze uthole iphrofayili yakho yobungozi futhi ubone iziphakamiso eziqondanisiwe.\nImifanekiso ye-",
  "homeTourStepStrategiesTitle": "",
